,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實編劇講情<br />\n生離死別真係老撚土到on9 <br />\n<br />\n反而今集 <br />\n雷神睇化放任洛基<br />\n但係洛基又唔想雷神完全唔管 <br />\n<br />\n呢啲先係有啲兄弟情味道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nloki都話正路應該係老豆死左令兩兄弟走返埋一齊呢d老土野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過loki心底裡都想佢阿哥管下佢呢段真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd6a3e096d7e7f252dd75fa712d310fc0f1ea64","tid":448944,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"1. 唔係齋電, 有D有色汁液會入左血管<br />\n2. MARVEL電影個世界觀D神係外星人黎, 住唔同星球<br />\n3. 不願致評"},{"pid":"8cac264fb7142ca793de02e02de23e2f95bd25ed","tid":448944,"uid":80566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"今次真係Loki表現最吸引人嘅一套戲<br />\n係Loki同Thor嘅相處入面都有好多同以前MCU嘅戲link埋嘅位 令成個表達更加自然<br />\n例如AVG1 Thor話Loki adopted&rarr;今集輪到Loki唔認Thor自己話自己adopted<br />\nLoki比Hulk撻&rarr;Thor比Hulk撻<br />\nLoki多次背叛Thor&rarr;Thor終於識玩返Loki轉頭<br />\n<br />\n其他仲有Odin臨死時Thor以為個海係Loki幻術，Hela話Loki口氣似足Odin，Thor搵野掟Loki幻影，Thor講8歲往事（幾千歲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n有種始於係家人，係兄弟 嘅感覺<br />\n最後Loki接住粒石兩個和好個度真係好warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好鍾意個幕<br />\n<br />\n但其實有少少唔明點解偷飛船個度Loki明明想出Thor但之後到咗聖域又咁落心落力幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個轉變好似快咗啲"},{"pid":"9f6499300333954390b8a61c9ce3d6084ec2b6fd","tid":448944,"uid":80566,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次真係Loki表現最吸引人嘅一套戲<br />\n係Loki同Thor嘅相處入面都有好多同以前MCU嘅戲link埋嘅位 令成個表達更加自然<br />\n例如AVG1 Thor話Loki adopted&rarr;今集輪到Loki唔認Thor自己話自己adopted<br />\nLoki比Hulk撻&rarr;Thor比Hulk撻<br />\nLoki多次背叛Thor&rarr;Thor終於識玩返Loki轉頭<br />\n<br />\n其他仲有Odin臨死時Thor以為個海係Loki幻術，Hela話Loki口氣似足Odin，Thor搵野掟Loki幻影，Thor講8歲往事（幾千歲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n有種始於係家人，係兄弟 嘅感覺<br />\n最後Loki接住粒石兩個和好個度真係好warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好鍾意個幕<br />\n<br />\n但其實有少少唔明點解偷飛船個度Loki明明想出<span style=\"color: red;\">賣</span>Thor但之後到咗聖域又咁落心落力幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個轉變好似快咗啲</blockquote><br />\n補返個字<span style=\"font-size: small;\">同埋唔好意思又中又英好似好難睇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"1f17b1cbc15626b15976d29dc86eac8cd1863e4f","tid":448944,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:16:07.000Z","msg":"marvel 今次你贏嗱 <br />\n首BGM 仲係我個腦到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20aca987f09c0cd2262870ae8aed084ee9060754","tid":448944,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:19:21.000Z","msg":"BGM都關編劇事？"},{"pid":"97f6aded39e9f4658de16caf7afa3e51f7659ef5","tid":448944,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BGM都關編劇事？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmarvel 一路都比人屌 <br />\n冇首 BGM 係記得 <br />\n<br />\n神話配歌劇 BGM 最正路 <br />\n用電音真係似突登 <br />\n咁岩果個星球都有玩電音 <br />\n<br />\nBGM 其實唔關編劇事<br />\n不過用岩 BGM 配岩劇情段落 <br />\n可以帶起觀眾情緒 <br />\n例子神奇女俠"},{"pid":"72d5c855506ee99077ea2dfb3eab543d9e006e81","tid":448944,"uid":2380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>marvel 今次你贏嗱 <br />\n首BGM 仲係我個腦到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牙吖呀~~~吖"},{"pid":"f03ceac44a484852efe91280b477730ebfbda2a2","tid":448944,"uid":55228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"第一集黎到地球俾人電暈入廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efcaaa0b917b2cfb3afac3f5e86ae7f72eb8cc6","tid":448944,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T00:56:56.000Z","msg":"<b